[size=14pt][b]Why Quantum Resistance Matters NOW[/b][/size]

[b]The "Store Now, Decrypt Later" Attack[/b]
Adversaries are already recording encrypted blockchain traffic. When quantum computers arrive (est. 2030-2035), they'll decrypt historical data. Your transactions from 2024 will be exposed in 2030.

[b]Our Solution:[/b]
[list]
[*]Hybrid post-quantum + classical cryptography deployed [b]today[/b]
[*]Protects historical data from future quantum attacks
[*]Seamless migration path through Phase 1 → 2 → 3 → 4
[/list]

